{"tid":1513340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"獨立調查先最重要!!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-28T09:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T09:50:22.000Z","uid":313627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c67bd5bb236fee069796dc8663753a90ec218eb5","tid":1513340,"uid":313627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:40:20.000Z","msg":"雖然一路都話五大訴求，缺一不可，但係我覺得點都會有啲係比較重要。雙普選固然重要，甚至可以話係今次事件嘅核心問題 (如果夠表否決嘅話根本唔會發生612 及之後嘅衝突)，但係根本無可能係短時間內推到。而撤回條例同暴動定性對改變現時局面無太大嘅幫助，只係得到精神上嘅勝利。所以我覺得最重要嘅都係獨立調查同釋放義士。<br />\n<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會呢個訴求係最多人讚成，有唔少建制派同商家都認同呢個訴求(商會、田北晨及民建聯部分人士等)。所以我覺得可以重點推呢個訴求，由其是向淺藍同嗰D 只想安穩不理政治嘅人， 可以試吓滲入吓藍絲D page。<br />\n<br />\n如果個post 係讚緊狗維持治安，就可以講吓 [我地行得正，點會怕獨立調查] 或者[<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持獨立獨查，還警隊清白</span></strong>] ，只有獨立調查，社會先至會有可能平靜。 總之要佢地覺得獨立調查點計都有佢地著數!!!<br />\n<br />\n附上對付各種藍絲嘅攻略: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2179701742127792&amp;id=347912661973385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2179701742127792%26id%3D347912661973385&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5DH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=a40c3b17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2179701742127792&amp;id=347912661973385</a> <br />\n(個人認為分析得唔錯，可根據此作戰略調整，加強攻擊力)<br />\n<br />\n要有咗獨立調查，先有希望可以釋放義士。目標係要黃藍都 We Connect!! 按政府邏輯，有47慢人出席撐警集會，即係仲有 700萬係唔撐㗎㗎啦~~ 所以其實我地贏面好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d13de8b15e46280ace35e87b94bdd17d03201df","tid":1513340,"uid":313627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"419c1253403a00e05355ec5bd198b4d106d82562","tid":1513340,"uid":313627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf459eb0ef372da6b1b4a7121d363d96d5da5bd7","tid":1513340,"uid":313627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:49:39.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"4ede813f6afa7655b9747a0de5fb3e10c9bfce0b","tid":1513340,"uid":313627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pwd8XxX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwd8XxX.jpg&h=6bb4b7b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b434e8a8dc7cb3563932a3976d9e1d1111a7e50e","tid":1513340,"uid":313627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0HNmx6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0HNmx6q.jpg&h=83bbe041&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}